            "title": "滬股半日高位收市   深股報跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股個別發展，滬股升深股跌，兩市合計成交13209.22億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日報3922，升9點或0.23%，以半日高位收市，早段見3872，跌41點或1.05%，為半日低位，即反覆向上，後段轉跌為升，半日成交5765.81億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日報13743，跌16點或0.12%，中段見13536，挫224點或1.63%，為半日低位，跌幅其後收窄，最高見13745，跌15點或0.11%，半日成交7443.41億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日報3279，跌16點或0.5%，滬深300半日報4495，跌6點或0.15%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15811210-%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%a0%b1%e8%b7%8c",
