            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段跟隨外圍下跌，上證綜指以3884點開市，跌29點或0.75%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報13618點，亦跌141點或1.03%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌40點或0.91%，開報4461點；創業板指數開市報3254點，跌41點或1.26%。</p>\n</div>",
